summary: An Ordinance authorizing the Mayor and City Comptroller to issue Local Improvement Bonds for the improvement of Fifteenth Avenue Northwest, from West 67th Street to West 67th Street, et al in the City of Seattle, by grading under Ordinance No. 24848, creating Local Improvement District No. 2388 prescribing the rate of interest thereon and authorizing their delivery to the contractor constructing the improvement.
